<sect2 role="platform">
<title>Platform and Architecture </title>
<para>This is the first section requiring knowledge of the target platform. For this 
book we will be using the Malta development board. By reviewing the initial config file 
for this platform we can determine that the architecture is MIPS.</para>
 
<screen os="c"><userinput>
cp &kernel_config; ${CLFS}/boot/config-&linux-version;

CLFS_ARCH=&clfs_arch;
echo export  CLFS_ARCH=&clfs_arch; >> ~/.bashrc

</userinput></screen>
</sect2>

